description: Dara Calleary says he should not have attended the event following a tightening of the rules.
title: Coronavirus: Irish agriculture minister apologises for event attendance
title_page: Coronavirus: Irish agriculture minister apologises for event attendance - BBC News
maintext: "I wish to apologise unreservedly to the public, from whom we are asking quite a lot at this difficult time. I also offer this apology and my sincere regret to my government colleagues."
